{
  "name": "RPlog_In_the_Jungle",
  "title": "Escape Through the Sith-Held Jungle",
  "summary": "After fleeing Sith droids in the streets of Tof Soren on the newly conquered world of Ord Vaxal, the Sullustan agent Enb'Zik and his Horansi wife Snarl meet their contact Aldol-Eo Pold, who confirms that Zik's enslaved family members were shipped offworld and provides an old Chariot speeder for their escape to Zik's grounded ship, Ranger One. Under the command of the droid General Siege and Captain Cato observing from orbit, a legion of speeder-mounted battle droids pursues the pair as they race for the jungle, their stray fire endangering civilians in the city. Zik pilots evasively while Snarl picks off the closing droids with her A280, decapitating one mid-leap and hurling its body to destroy another, as Zik blasts through trees and leaps the speeder across a bombardment crater. Threading blast radii left from an old orbital bombardment, the couple rouse Ranger One by coded signal and order it ready for flight, only to find as they near the clearing that a fallen tree has crashed against the ship and blocked its main hatch.",
